<%# Tui::SyncIndicatorComponent — 3-state sync indicator for TST.
    NO brackets, NO glyphs — just the word "sync" with color states.
      synced       — muted color, no animation
      syncing      — accent color + shimmer animation
      disconnected — danger red, no animation
    The word's letters scramble (4-char) on state transitions (240ms).
    JS drives transitions via pito:cable-activity + tui:sync-changed. %>
<span class="tui-sync-indicator is-<%= initial_state %>"
      data-controller="tui-sync-indicator"
      data-tui-sync-indicator-state-value="<%= initial_state %>">sync</span>
